{"tid":1538522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"合理懷疑 強姦/殺人係真事 林鄭用最無力既一樣黎降溫/分化","createTime":"2019-09-04T07:13:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T13:46:22.000Z","uid":60006,"like":50,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"1b2b0a595def2ffeb271c37878b9c49b3ff0a0fd","tid":1538522,"uid":60006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:13:14.000Z","msg":"首先呢個女人幾惡毒 有幾多心計大家都好清楚<br />\n<br />\n如果黑警公安武警 殺人/強姦係真既話 <br />\n唔洗等到10月1 或者星期六日 第二日一定遍地開花 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而班狗已經無力再handle 8月5個日既規模<br />\n如果兩單傳聞是但一單係真既話 開花既威力同規模一定再大幾倍, 班狗一定要開實彈先保到命<br />\n<br />\n同時亦都可以想像一定會有白警走出黎 <br />\n白警唔洗多 有10個行出黎影張相 威力已經係原子彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁係發展成咁之前 做5大訴求最無力個條<br />\n等少咁一班人, 怒火亦降低既時候 <br />\n先慢慢同家屬deal/威嚇<br />\n到真係cum唔住再爆既時候 威力一定無咁大"},{"pid":"9a2f187cd7b5588897e62c668cf16309be07a651","tid":1538522,"uid":60006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:17:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ac9a142a98ee48f14b835c4fd4abd6c171b24ff9","tid":1538522,"uid":60006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:19:00.000Z","msg":"班狗又自認想強姦"},{"pid":"20f1bb1cca0bee6a3a5b3421d3f3f7dfb0e51b10","tid":1538522,"uid":202724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:21:13.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47aba21948fc83c61a93bf50f2814eb1a0491274","tid":1538522,"uid":295304,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:25:55.000Z","msg":"有冇見過兇殺案由政府新聞處公佈？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1535010\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1535010</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n睇埋回覆先留言，因為分析我放咗喺回覆<br />\n<br />\n成個熱門勁多都係講林鄭撤回嘅風，<br />\n但而家佢撤唔撤回都好，831太子站有冇死人、有冇極嚴重傷勢受害人，呢d都係要查啊！唔好俾佢轉移焦點啊！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好認真，點解一路發生咁多件事，都冇話撤回，突然今日會講起？到底呢幾日發生咗咩事逼到佢要做野？係咪真係其實死咗人？就算冇死人，到底情況係幾嚴重？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要求黨鐵交出831太子站完整CCTV記錄啊！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"2cdc4e8d7ee221db198b22804a6ff21c6e318b7d","tid":1538522,"uid":60006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:53:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0570c2000601656d94147769ba700ee96eae50d7","tid":1538522,"uid":60006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:56:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"42c32c5e2ff13cd2bbd99dbc0a637865fc1af656","tid":1538522,"uid":51790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:57:18.000Z","msg":"同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"555dfbdf0e28cdefb72fcfcf8e2c714122e33c27","tid":1538522,"uid":60006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:03:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1de877c284e65329cb1c77a839a53e215d2cf9d7","tid":1538522,"uid":80015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:05:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94a8c2ad029d5fb9a682bdc6eacc4b7f919c9d9b","tid":1538522,"uid":72800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:09:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xcgb58P.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxcgb58P.gif&h=4c045c7d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ep8qq8P.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEp8qq8P.gif&h=b74f62eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong><em><div style=\"text-align: center;\">毋忘七烈 千一義 四眼 三十骨折 手腳筋<br />\n721元朗 811警暴 831車廂 雙肺 一裙<br />\n無數屈辱私刑 重傷昏迷<br />\n<br />\n撤回 定性 釋士 究警 普選</div></em></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港共殺人政權企圖以<strong>錄音、撤回、學季開始</strong><br />\n轉移<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">太子地鐵傷亡、<br />\n六警壓脊椎休克 至今嚴重昏迷、<br />\n新屋嶺、民主人權法案</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>核彈</strong></span><span style=\"color: red;\">事件焦點<br />\n醒呀大家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政府帶緊風向</span><br />\n背後繼續大清算 入獄 利刑 一年後被失蹤</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">暗黑兵法劇本 出沒注意：\n\n沒收gear 未來兩星期大量武警喬裝示威者 嫁禍衝擊\n內部分化示威者、\n酷刑凌虐威嚇被捕人士、\n邊緣打壓香港 渲染港獨 阻抗爭之風蔓延內陸、\n假新聞、擺拍、編輯、洗腦文宣製造風向 污名化運動、\n暴力鎮壓 拘捕 扣留 私刑 企圖瓦解前線、\n文宣 抹黑 嫁禍 插贜 示威者、\n暗殺 第一滴血 企圖逆轉民意 國際譴責、\n市民絕望噤聲 憤怒冷卻、\n中立派 賺錢派 政治疲勞、\n鼓吹經濟下滑風向 富豪商家屈服 加速瓦解、\n學季始開，拖延 分散 擊破、\n白色恐怖、清除異己、染紅香港\n\n拖字訣 雨傘結局 ⋯</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n袋住先 放風降溫<br />\n大追捕 清算 正式開始<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>這不只是反修例活動<br />\n這是屬於香港人的<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時代革命</span></strong></span></div>"},{"pid":"bc771ab3f280a21ac58361e9040b47e5c0824707","tid":1538522,"uid":60006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:12:09.000Z","msg":"[重組傳聞] 女示威者被強姦 武警公安混入警隊 同新屋嶺事件<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533609\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533609</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7dd42a3cbc9290a58e6192ac43a42222f5ce75d7","tid":1538522,"uid":241904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:13:26.000Z","msg":"佢而家撤回根本係想我地8/9少人出黎,咁9/9美國復會就未必過到香港人權關係法<br />\n撤回係3個月前既訴求<br />\n而家係五大訴求,缺一不可<br />\n如果唔係只會每幾年就有一過revolution"},{"pid":"c93742632a72aa51613a4f53b08779fba75c08d5","tid":1538522,"uid":60006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:17:14.000Z","msg":"[重組傳聞] 女示威者被強姦 武警公安混入警隊 同新屋嶺事件<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533609\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533609</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4d9dcb97c2f45a0d5c01df6